      @Then("I Assert that the element found by {string}: {string}, exactly matches with the expected reference image using Artificial Intelligence (OpenCV)") public void assertElementMatchesOpenCV​(java.lang.String locatorType, java.lang.String locatorValue)
      Asserts that the current image of the target element matches the expected reference image using the desired VisualValidationEngine if AssertionType is POSITIVE, or doesn't match it if AssertionType is NEGATIVE.
